/path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><span class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold text-white/90\">Together, We Can</span></div><h1 class=\"font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6.5xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-wide text-shadow-md\">Lighting Lives. <br/>Transforming Communities. <br/>Creating <span class=\"text-gold\">Futures.</span></h1><p class=\"text-base sm:text-lg text-white/80 max-w-xl font-normal leading-relaxed text-shadow-sm font-sans\">We work in education, healthcare, renewable energy and community development to build a better, brighter and equitable India.</p></div><div class=\"hidden lg:block lg:col-span-5\"></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 md:mt-16 flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between gap-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 w-full z-30\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0\"><a href=\"#projects\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-white text-navy font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/95 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group/btn\"><span>Explore Our Impact</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-navy transition-transform duration-300 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#projects\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full border border-white/40 bg-transparent text-white font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/60 hover:scale-105 group/btn2\"><span>View Projects</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-play w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-white text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover/btn2:scale-110\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 5a2 2 0 0 1 3.008-1.728l11.997 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"w-full lg:w-auto bg-[#121212]/85 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/15 py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl lg:max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6 items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 pl-2 first:pl-0 md:border-l md:border-white/10 md:first:border-0 md:pl-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight font-serif text-white leading-none mb-1\">25,000+</div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-white/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider leading-snug truncate\">Lives Impacted</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 pl-2 first:pl-0 md:border-l md:border-white/10 md:first:border-0 md:pl-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-house w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8\"></path><path d=\"M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-6a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 6A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight font-serif text-white leading-none mb-1\">100+</div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-white/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider leading-snug truncate\">Villages Reached</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 pl-2 first:pl-0 md:border-l md:border-white/10 md:first:border-0 md:pl-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight font-serif text-white leading-none mb-1\">50+</div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-white/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider leading-snug truncate\">Education Initiatives</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 pl-2 first:pl-0 md:border-l md:border-white/10 md:first:border-0 md:pl-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-yellow-500 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><div class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight font-serif text-white leading-none mb-1\">10+</div><div class=\"text-[9px] text-white/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider leading-snug truncate\">Renewable Energy Projects</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"why-we-exist\" class=\"bg-beige py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-20 items-end\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Why We Exist</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">We Envision An India Where Every Child Has The Chance To Dream And Achieve.</h2></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-base leading-relaxed\">For generations, lack of basic needs has created barriers for remote communities. We believe that by solving education, healthcare, and energy gaps simultaneously, we trigger permanent, generational transformation.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-[52px] left-[calc(100%-20px)] w-[calc(100%-80px)] z-0 pointer-events-none\"><svg class=\"w-full h-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 20\"><path d=\"M0,10 Q25,18 50,10 T100,10\" stroke=\"#166534\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,4\" fill=\"none\" class=\"opacity-40\"></path><polygon points=\"98,10 93,7 93,13\" fill=\"#166534\" class=\"opacity-40\"></polygon></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-red-50 text-red-600 border-red-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-alert w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12.01\" y1=\"16\" y2=\"16\"></line></svg></div><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-navy/10 group-hover:text-gold/20 transition-colors duration-300\">01</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-navy\">The Problem</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Millions of children and families lack access to quality education, basic healthcare, clean water, and stable electricity in remote villages across India, holding back their human potential.</p></div></div><a class=\"pt-8 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-forest group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/about\"><span>Explore approach</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-[52px] left-[calc(100%-20px)] w-[calc(100%-80px)] z-0 pointer-events-none\"><svg class=\"w-full h-8\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 20\"><path d=\"M0,10 Q25,18 50,10 T100,10\" stroke=\"#166534\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,4\" fill=\"none\" class=\"opacity-40\"></path><polygon points=\"98,10 93,7 93,13\" fill=\"#166534\" class=\"opacity-40\"></polygon></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 border-emerald-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-navy/10 group-hover:text-gold/20 transition-colors duration-300\">02</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-navy\">Our Action</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">We implement holistic, sustainable projects locally—renovating classrooms, holding medical checkup initiatives, installing solar power plants, and building community-led programs.</p></div></div><a class=\"pt-8 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-forest group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/about\"><span>Explore approach</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl border border-navy/5 p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.05)] transition-all duration-500 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 border-amber-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-navy/10 group-hover:text-gold/20 transition-colors duration-300\">03</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-navy\">The Impact</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed\">We create a lasting ecosystem that empowers children to dream, supports healthy livelihoods, preserves natural environments, and builds resilient, self-sufficient communities.</p></div></div><a class=\"pt-8 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-forest group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/about\"><span>Explore approach</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"impact\" class=\"relative bg-forest text-white py-20 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-5 select-none pointer-events-none\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><pattern id=\"grid\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><path d=\"M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\"></path></pattern></defs><rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#grid)\"></rect></svg></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gold uppercase block\">Measurable Change</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight\">Our Work in Numbers</h2><p class=\"text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base\">Every statistic represents a human life touched, a student empowered, or a village lit. We verify our metrics independently to ensure clean, transparent accountability.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center backdrop-blur-sm flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-serif text-gold mb-3 flex items-center justify-center\"><span>0</span><span>+</span></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2\">Lives Impacted</h3></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-xs md:text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Individuals empowered across various programs</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center backdrop-blur-sm flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-serif text-gold mb-3 flex items-center justify-center\"><span>0</span><span>+</span></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2\">Villages Reached</h3></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-xs md:text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Rural habitations connected and supported</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center backdrop-blur-sm flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-serif text-gold mb-3 flex items-center justify-center\"><span>0</span><span>+</span></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2\">Students Educated</h3></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-xs md:text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Children receiving quality, modern education</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center backdrop-blur-sm flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-serif text-gold mb-3 flex items-center justify-center\"><span>0</span><span>+</span></div><h3 class=\"font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-2\">Healthcare Beneficiaries</h3></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-xs md:text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed\">Received free medical diagnostic &amp; checkups</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"projects\" class=\"bg-beige/40 py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-4 max-w-2xl\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Our Initiatives</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">Featured Projects Making Real Difference.</h2></div><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-xs mt-4 md:mt-0 leading-relaxed\">Focused on building clean energy foundations and providing critical healthcare checkups directly where resources are scarce.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12\"><div id=\"project-odisha\" class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-navy/5 shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(15,23,42,0.02)] hover:shadow-[0_30px_70px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)] transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div><div class=\"relative aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden w-full\"><img alt=\"Odisha Solar Plant Project\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_odisha_solar.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-navy/30 via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><span class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm text-navy text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm\">📍 <!-- -->Odisha</span><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 max-w-[70%] justify-end\"><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Renewable Energy</span><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Infrastructure</span><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Sustainability</span></div></div><div class=\"p-8 sm:p-10 space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy group-hover:text-forest transition-colors duration-300\">Odisha Solar Plant Project</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Providing clean, sustainable and affordable energy to rural tribal communities through localized solar micro-grids. We light up households, schools, and health centers, paving the way for economic activity after sunset.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-navy/5\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">50+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Villages</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">5MW+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Solar Capacity</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">15,000+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Lives Impacted</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"px-8 pb-8 sm:px-10 sm:pb-10 pt-2\"><button class=\"relative w-44 h-12 bg-navy text-white rounded-full p-1.5 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-start shadow-md hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-300 group/btn cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-white text-navy flex items-center justify-center z-20 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"absolute right-6 font-semibold text-sm select-none z-10\">Read More</span></button></div></div><div id=\"project-delhi\" class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-navy/5 shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(15,23,42,0.02)] hover:shadow-[0_30px_70px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)] transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div><div class=\"relative aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden w-full\"><img alt=\"Delhi Medical Checkup Initiative\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-navy/30 via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><span class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm text-navy text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm\">📍 <!-- -->Delhi</span><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 max-w-[70%] justify-end\"><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Healthcare</span><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Community Development</span><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Emergency Relief</span></div></div><div class=\"p-8 sm:p-10 space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy group-hover:text-forest transition-colors duration-300\">Delhi Medical Checkup Initiative</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Free health checkups, diagnostics, expert consultations, and essential medicine distribution for underserved urban slum communities in Delhi and nearby suburban clusters.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-navy/5\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">20,000+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Beneficiaries</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">100+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Health Camps</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">50+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Communities</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"px-8 pb-8 sm:px-10 sm:pb-10 pt-2\"><button class=\"relative w-44 h-12 bg-navy text-white rounded-full p-1.5 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-start shadow-md hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-300 group/btn cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-white text-navy flex items-center justify-center z-20 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"absolute right-6 font-semibold text-sm select-none z-10\">Read More</span></button></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center mt-16\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-3 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-forest text-white font-semibold text-sm transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-forest/90 shadow-md\" href=\"/projects\"><span>View All Projects</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-navy text-white py-24 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-20\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl space-y-6\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gold uppercase block\">Interactive Reach Map</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight\">Explore Our Project Footprint Across India</h2><p class=\"text-white/70 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-sans\">Visualize where Face of Change installs solar micro-grids, hosts community diagnostic clinics, and reforms classrooms. Toggle active states on our digital map dashboard.</p><div class=\"pt-2\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-2.5 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-gold text-navy font-semibold text-sm transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-gold/90 shadow-[0_4px_14px_rgba(245,158,11,0.3)]\" href=\"/impact\"><span>Open Interactive Map</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map w-4 h-4 text-navy fill-navy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.106 5.553a2 2 0 0 0 1.788 0l3.659-1.83A1 1 0 0 1 21 4.619v12.764a1 1 0 0 1-.553.894l-4.553 2.277a2 2 0 0 1-1.788 0l-4.212-2.106a2 2 0 0 0-1.788 0l-3.659 1.83A1 1 0 0 1 3 19.381V6.618a1 1 0 0 1 .553-.894l4.553-2.277a2 2 0 0 1 1.788 0z\"></path><path d=\"M15 5.764v15\"></path><path d=\"M9 3.236v15\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"media\" class=\"bg-[#FAF9F5] py-24 md:py-32 border-b border-navy/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-10\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-forest uppercase block\">Media That Recognizes Change</span><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between gap-6\"><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5.5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">News &amp; Media Coverage</h2><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-sm max-w-xl leading-relaxed\">From local stories to national headlines — see how our work is creating real impact across India.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-start\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-12 space-y-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8\"><article class=\"bg-white border border-navy/5 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)] hover:border-navy/10 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 pb-4 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center h-10\"><span class=\"font-serif font-black italic tracking-tighter text-navy border-y border-navy/30 py-0.5 px-3 text-[13px] leading-none uppercase select-none \">THE HINDU</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-[10px] text-navy/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span>12 May 2024</span><span class=\"text-navy/15\">•</span><span>THE HINDU</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-base text-navy leading-snug hover:text-forest transition-colors\">Solar Power, Brighter Futures: Transforming Rural Odisha</h3><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 pt-1\"><span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[9px] font-bold border uppercase bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 border-orange-100/50\">Odisha</span><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-xs leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Solar power brings new hope to 500+ families in rural Odisha.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-navy/5 mt-4\"><a href=\"https://thehindu.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-gold transition-colors\"><span>Read Full Article</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-navy/5 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)] hover:border-navy/10 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 pb-4 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center h-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center font-serif text-navy select-none \"><div class=\"border-y border-navy/30 py-0.5 px-2\"><span class=\"text-[7px] font-bold tracking-[0.18em] block uppercase leading-none mb-0.5\">THE TIMES OF</span><span class=\"text-xs font-black tracking-wider block uppercase leading-none\">INDIA</span></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-[10px] text-navy/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span>05 May 2024</span><span class=\"text-navy/15\">•</span><span>THE TIMES OF INDIA</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-base text-navy leading-snug hover:text-forest transition-colors\">Health for All: Free Medical Camps in Delhi&#x27;s Communities</h3><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 pt-1\"><span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[9px] font-bold border uppercase bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-100/50\">Delhi</span><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-xs leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Medical checkup initiative reaches 20,000+ people across Delhi.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-navy/5 mt-4\"><a href=\"https://timesofindia.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-gold transition-colors\"><span>Read Full Article</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-navy/5 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)] hover:border-navy/10 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 pb-4 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center h-10\"><span class=\"font-sans font-bold text-slate-700 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-wide select-none \">दैनिक जागरण</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-[10px] text-navy/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span>20 Apr 2024</span><span class=\"text-navy/15\">•</span><span>दैनिक जागरण</span></div><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-base text-navy leading-snug hover:text-forest transition-colors\">बेहतर शिक्षा के लिए बदलते क्लासरूम, बदलते बच्चों के सपने</h3><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 pt-1\"><span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[9px] font-bold border uppercase bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 border-sky-100/50\">Education</span><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-xs leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Classroom transformation program improving education in government schools.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-navy/5 mt-4\"><a href=\"https://jagran.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold text-forest uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-gold transition-colors\"><span>Read Full Article</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></article></div><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-forest text-white font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-forest/90 transition-colors shadow-sm group\" href=\"/media\"><span>View All Media Coverage</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-beige/40 py-24 border-t border-b border-navy/5\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-8\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Join Our Journey</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">Partner with us to create sustainable, lasting change.</h2><p class=\"text-navy/60 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-sans\">Whether you are a corporation looking for CSR projects, an institution looking to sponsor classrooms, or an individual contributor — let&#x27;s build a better India together.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-2\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-between px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-navy text-white font-semibold text-sm transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 shadow-md group/cbtn\" href=\"/contact\"><span>CSR &amp; General Inquiry</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-l